rows.label: qev055805_MSG0002
rows.name:
If friend borrow money, friend must pay it back.
That just common sense, but Noborata show no sign
of repaying Tikotiko.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055805_MSG0003
rows.name:
Dumb Noborata probably blew it all on pizza.
And Tikotiko didn't get single slice![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055805_MSG0006
rows.name:
Min'barac not like no-good Noborata.
Min'barac will definitely pay debts.
Tikotiko happy to have reasonable friend for once![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055805_MSG0007
rows.name:
Tikotiko heard friend was looking for jagged mortars.
Caravan friend of Tikotiko saw one at Northpointe
Cove.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055805_MSG0008
rows.name:
As a special onetime service, that tip was free.
Now hurry up and go get mortars![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055805_MSG0009
rows.name:
Min'barac not rowdy like Selia or unreliable like
Noborata.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055805_MSG0010
rows.name:
Tikotiko know we will be good friends,
but Min'barac need to stay alive first![ST:wait ]
